        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Map 1: Distributions of species of the Ischnosoma spelaeum group in the Caucasus region, based on revised and reliable records: I. caucasicum (white circles); I. barbigerum (black triangle); I. acutum (white diamonds); I. myops (black circles). Grey circle: doubtful locality “Helenendorf” (today Göygöl)." ;
